# Removes input permute since preprocessing now provides NCHW layout directly.
# Rewrites the pose-decode to be fp16/NPU-safe. The original decode flattened the
# 48x48 feature map and ran argmax over H*W (indices up to 2303), then rebuilt
# (y, x) via div/mod. On the NPU (fp16) integers above 2048 are not exact, so
# any peak in the bottom rows decoded to the wrong coordinate. The fix uses a
# separable 2-D argmax (coords stay <= 47, exact in fp16) and reads values with
# permute+matmul ops (QNN DLC compatible). Bit-exact with the original in fp32.
#
